-1310481470.text: "Direct inhibition of calcineurin with FK506 XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, cyclosporine A (CsA) XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR, or RNAi mediated depletion of the calcineurin catalytic subunit (PPP3CB) was also sufficient to block TFEB activation by AD, suggesting small-molecule inhibition of PTPMT1 activates TFEB via mobilization of calcineurin catalytic activity."
